Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,------------SUB-----------
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.04,0:00:07.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此  我们来决定一下本班的出展项目吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.96,0:00:10.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁有什么主意吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.25,0:00:12.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  我想演戏
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.19,0:00:14.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鬼屋之类的也不错吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.06,0:00:16.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可丽饼店
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.43,0:00:18.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样的话就普通点搞个烧烤店之类的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.66,0:00:20.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师  老师  老师
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.65,0:00:25.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师觉得「心跳！帅哥多多的露天啤酒店」不错啦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.90,0:00:27.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师请闭嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.99,0:00:30.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裕君好冷漠
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.51,0:00:34.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前还说长大了要当由香里姐姐的老公
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.82,0:00:37.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,独占那南国水果一般的丰满身材…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.94,0:00:42.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可丽饼店和烧烤店
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.15,0:00:43.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有其他吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.82,0:00:46.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  Cosplay咖啡店如何
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.89,0:00:50.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Cosplay咖啡…咦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.15,0:00:56.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Cosplay咖啡店就是Cosplay后的店员来接客的咖啡店
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.79,0:00:59.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正菜单里有可丽饼和烧烤也没什么问题
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.94,0:01:02.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又可以像鬼屋一样做各种装扮
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.66,0:01:05.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还可以像演戏一般扮演各种角色
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.86,0:01:08.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐呐  不觉得很赞么
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.73,0:01:12.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说  为什么隔壁班的你会在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.04,0:01:16.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  这些小事情就不要在意了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.28,0:01:18.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如何嘛  Cosplay咖啡店
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.18,0:01:23.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是像在秋叶原流行的女仆咖啡店之类的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.91,0:01:26.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是能穿可爱的衣服倒是不错
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.40,0:01:27.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男生要干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.63,0:01:31.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然  要是让女生穿的话我推荐学校泳装
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.26,0:01:34.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我绝对不认同旧学校泳装之外的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.54,0:01:38.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  朴素的水手服也会让人耳目一新
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.48,0:01:41.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那么就让我们投票决定吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.62,0:01:47.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正如各位所见  出展项目决定为Cosplay咖啡店了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.78,0:01:51.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家一起开心地办好Cosplay咖啡店吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.66,0:01:57.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样一来出展项目也决定好了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.52,0:01:58.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,执行委员  加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.98,0:02:00.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.00,0:03:42.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,班里的出展项目决定好了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.38,0:03:45.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是到头来还是采用了信长的主意啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.21,0:03:49.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  要是那么想搞Cosplay咖啡店的话
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.17,0:03:51.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在自己的班里搞不就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.69,0:03:53.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在班里也提过了的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.97,0:03:55.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过以小差距输了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.18,0:03:57.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以想在裕人的班里复仇
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.85,0:04:01.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么这会叫复仇啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.32,0:04:04.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Cosplay咖啡店不是很有趣的样子吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.89,0:04:06.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎光临
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.55,0:04:12.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好  能穿上什么衣服呢  好期待啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.44,0:04:15.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过  虽然决定是Cosplay咖啡店了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.85,0:04:17.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我也不太懂啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.89,0:04:19.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.36,0:04:22.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我本想着是像秋叶原的女仆咖啡店一般的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.64,0:04:24.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,信长却说不是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.07,0:04:28.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且我根本就不太懂Cosplay和咖啡店
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.45,0:04:30.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该怎么办呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.15,0:04:34.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裕人  那个…我…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.35,0:04:40.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裕人裕人  执行委员要到会议室集合了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.83,0:04:43.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉春香  之后再说了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.75,0:04:46.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点快点  乃木坂同学  对不起了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.85,0:04:47.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.35,0:04:48.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.08,0:04:56.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乃木坂前辈今年也参加白凤祭的选美吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.09,0:05:00.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前辈要是参加的话  就一定是二连霸了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.39,0:05:01.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  我…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.38,0:05:16.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乃木坂前辈  怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.94,0:05:18.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.15,0:05:39.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大哥哥当执行委员吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.20,0:05:41.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  虽然看起来很辛苦的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.66,0:05:42.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过他很努力
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.02,0:05:46.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是既然如此的话  要是姐姐是搭档就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.74,0:05:48.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油做好执行委员
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.33,0:05:50.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两人的距离闪电拉近之类的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.77,0:05:52.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千载难逢的机会
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.42,0:05:55.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  说什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.08,0:05:57.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么  我们自言自语
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.40,0:06:01.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那姐姐就是在背后支持着大哥哥  对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.02,0:06:10.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.87,0:06:14.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我  我想如果能稍微帮上他的忙的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.94,0:06:17.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是一样贤淑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.18,0:06:20.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是还很天真哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.78,0:06:24.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必须得更积极地追求大哥哥才行
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.71,0:06:28.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,积极地？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.22,0:06:39.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此  第一次「大哥哥的心捕获大作战」会议现在开始
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.10,0:06:44.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做便当带去也很好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.89,0:06:48.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给他送亲手做的饼干和红茶套餐之类的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.44,0:06:50.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干脆绑架了他
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.33,0:06:54.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叶月  好主意
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.17,0:06:57.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用饼干去绑架？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.85,0:07:02.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其他还有问他「累了吗  裕人」之类的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.49,0:07:07.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帮  帮  帮他按摩
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.92,0:07:09.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美夏小姐太大胆了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.97,0:07:11.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太色了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.93,0:07:15.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这  这样的事情…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.46,0:07:17.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.04,0:07:21.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在白凤祭的最后一起跳土风舞
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.80,0:07:25.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,土风舞…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.10,0:07:41.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  裕  裕人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.60,0:07:42.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绫濑君吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.00,0:07:45.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才和椎菜一起出去了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.34,0:07:46.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像说有什么执行委员会之类的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.19,0:07:49.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.22,0:07:51.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  春香
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.65,0:07:53.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裕人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.17,0:07:56.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.93,0:07:59.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能跟我来一下吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.15,0:08:02.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的  什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.15,0:08:09.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  春香知不知道哪有卖Cosplay衣服的店子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.71,0:08:12.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想见识一下实物
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.86,0:08:17.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咖啡店的装潢和菜单倒是都基本想好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.98,0:08:21.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是关于Cosplay就完全着不了手
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.44,0:08:24.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在夏漫展的时候春香似乎又对Cosplay很有兴趣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.88,0:08:27.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想春香的话或许会知道
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.23,0:08:28.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是说…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.72,0:08:30.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…是的  我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.33,0:08:32.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.38,0:08:35.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上次跟裕人去秋叶原的时候见到过了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.02,0:08:37.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地址我也知道
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.51,0:08:38.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.55,0:08:42.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗  那这周的星期天能带我去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.28,0:08:44.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…是的  这周星期天对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.14,0:08:48.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星期天…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.46,0:08:49.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.97,0:08:54.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么  这周星期天对吧  我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.32,0:08:55.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.49,0:08:59.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得救了  这样的话Cosplay咖啡店也总算能弄妥了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.46,0:09:05.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恭候您的光临  主人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.54,0:09:08.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人还是那么多啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.84,0:09:13.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,双休日人特别多  请注意不要走散哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.93,0:09:19.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香  你好像特别开心的样子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.06,0:09:22.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  很开心
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.67,0:09:23.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.55,0:09:36.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真厉害  这些全是Cosplay的衣服吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.44,0:09:40.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为这里也接受定做
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.20,0:09:41.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以这只是一小部分
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.16,0:09:42.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.43,0:09:47.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夜想曲女子学院长曲棍球部的冬装
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.79,0:09:50.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有笨拙女孩小秋的魔法服
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.34,0:09:53.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管哪个都好可爱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.90,0:09:56.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个太轻飘飘的了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.69,0:09:58.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毕竟是用来接客的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.78,0:10:00.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs20}是否方便活动呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.79,0:10:03.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对  对了  今天是为了看Cosplay咖啡店的服装来的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.97,0:10:08.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裕人  服装是由班里的大家来做吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.95,0:10:12.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  我想在这里看看实物来参考
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.99,0:10:14.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为没有给每人都买一套的预算
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.04,0:10:18.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样的话  这件如何
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.80,0:10:21.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魔法大餐的夏服版
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.51,0:10:24.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,制作方法简单  而且又方便活动
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.90,0:10:27.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这件不错啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.67,0:10:28.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.55,0:10:33.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这件是笨拙女孩小秋的天使版
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.48,0:10:36.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,制作方法似乎太复杂了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.76,0:10:39.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没问题的哦  做工意外地简单
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.00,0:10:41.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且不挑身材  大家应该都能穿上
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.12,0:10:47.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗  果然还是女孩子比较了解这些呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.34,0:10:49.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪  哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.28,0:10:51.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香也想穿穿这件吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.17,0:10:54.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  一定很开心的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.55,0:10:58.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这位客人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.26,0:11:01.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是有兴趣的话  可以试穿一下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.72,0:11:04.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,试  试穿？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.37,0:11:07.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中意的话  不妨就试穿一下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.79,0:11:10.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…那个…可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.76,0:11:12.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之先试穿一下看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.97,0:11:16.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…呃…那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.59,0:11:18.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想试穿一下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.73,0:11:21.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了  请到这边来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.00,0:11:24.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请进
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.43,0:11:30.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  那个…请稍等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.99,0:11:55.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没  没问题吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.40,0:12:01.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  裕人…呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.19,0:12:05.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  去买了参考资料…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.05,0:12:10.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那个  怎…怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.18,0:12:15.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裕…裕人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.80,0:12:20.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那个  非常适合你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.35,0:12:22.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.24,0:12:26.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  就像真正的天使一样
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.11,0:12:28.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之  很完美
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.67,0:12:31.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.24,0:12:38.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下午好  店长在吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.43,0:12:41.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.20,0:12:43.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裕…裕人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.85,0:12:45.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  紧急事态
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.01,0:12:47.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎光临  朝仓大人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.85,0:12:53.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  店长上次和你谈起的小皮罗的插肩袖的事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.00,0:12:56.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs20}是的  姑且是做出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.92,0:12:55.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好挤啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.37,0:12:57.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs20}怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.59,0:12:59.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs20}哦  还不错嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.67,0:13:03.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  在信长回去之前请忍耐下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.70,0:13:08.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春…春香
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.80,0:13:11.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裕…人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.00,0:13:17.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs20}那么  这件事就拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.40,0:13:18.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs20}我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.45,0:13:19.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs20}再见咯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.60,0:13:20.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs20}欢迎再次光临
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.43,0:13:28.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总  总之学到了不少
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.42,0:13:29.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你  春香
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.78,0:13:31.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没  不用这么客气
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.12,0:13:33.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微帮上你的忙了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.59,0:13:38.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不是一点点  帮大忙了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.83,0:13:40.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…是这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.89,0:13:43.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香  这个送你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.08,0:13:44.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.17,0:13:46.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打开看看
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.28,0:13:55.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这  这是笨拙女孩小秋的八音盒
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.76,0:13:59.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚刚看到的  作为今天的礼物
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.11,0:14:02.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,礼  礼物什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.48,0:14:05.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只不过是把你带到店里而已
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.49,0:14:09.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有这回事  你帮了大忙了  春香
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.76,0:14:12.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裕人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.51,0:14:15.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.92,0:14:19.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  美…美夏？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.72,0:14:21.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs20}性感的美夏
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.04,0:14:20.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么时候记下号码的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.31,0:14:23.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.56,0:14:26.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大哥哥  姐姐在你那里吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.14,0:14:29.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你  你现在在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.14,0:14:33.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起这个  快带着姐姐离开那里
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.50,0:14:34.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.27,0:14:36.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父亲往你们那里去了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.48,0:14:37.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玄冬先生？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.43,0:14:42.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在刚才带着HELL  HOUND出击了  不快点逃跑的话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.96,0:14:45.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以说  为什么要逃跑呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.21,0:14:47.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐今天和父亲约好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.39,0:14:52.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说是一个名叫波里尼的著名钢琴大师要见她
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.13,0:14:56.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本来定在今天  父亲也很期待着
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.18,0:14:58.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说…莫非
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.86,0:15:03.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐放了父亲鸽子  选择和大哥哥一起约会
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.14,0:15:05.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是被父亲发现了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.49,0:15:07.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.07,0:15:22.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被我找到了  果然和你这家伙在一起啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.47,0:15:23.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这个混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.32,0:15:26.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玄冬先生  春香她没有错
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.06,0:15:29.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,错的是强逼她约会的我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.91,0:15:30.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裕人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.92,0:15:34.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己承认自己的恶行  好胆量
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.94,0:15:36.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我咬紧牙关
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.93,0:15:38.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.87,0:15:46.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.08,0:15:48.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  来晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.71,0:15:56.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们  打算干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.42,0:15:58.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是我的请求  亲爱的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.67,0:16:01.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赶上了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.19,0:16:04.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  你这个人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.84,0:16:11.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每次都是这样一时头脑发热
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.01,0:16:14.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先听听他们俩怎么说吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.41,0:16:18.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么好听的  全都是那个混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.49,0:16:20.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请你先闭嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.28,0:16:24.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了春香  让我听听
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.94,0:16:28.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么擅自放弃了和波里尼老师的会面
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.20,0:16:31.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这…这是因为
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.74,0:16:33.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前和你说好的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.61,0:16:40.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要让我们承认你的兴趣  就要好好的学习
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.36,0:16:42.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次这样该怎么办呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.82,0:16:46.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很开心
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.25,0:16:47.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开心？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.48,0:16:51.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  因为是裕人第一次拜托我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.86,0:16:56.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想到能帮上裕人的忙  我就很开心
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.53,0:17:01.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我知道放弃和父亲的约定很不好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.46,0:17:05.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  今天对我来说是很重要的一天
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.24,0:17:08.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论如何我都想帮助裕人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.50,0:17:11.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以  错的人是我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.42,0:17:12.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  不是那样的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.49,0:17:14.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,错的人是我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.90,0:17:17.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有考虑到春香是否有空  硬是拜托她
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.81,0:17:21.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是  我是以自己的意愿选择了和裕人在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.94,0:17:22.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以说…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.45,0:17:24.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  就算是这样  也是我…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.37,0:17:26.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.31,0:17:27.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两个人到此为止
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.96,0:17:29.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,情况大致上了解了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.19,0:17:33.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有两人互相重视对方的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.19,0:17:40.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是这次的事给波里尼老师和父亲添了麻烦是事实
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.08,0:17:43.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也违反了和我所做的约定
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.99,0:17:45.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你明白了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.82,0:17:46.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.92,0:17:47.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.87,0:17:49.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…是的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.16,0:17:49.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.72,0:17:54.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的话  应该不会再发生同样的事情了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.64,0:17:58.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以  这次就看在两人之间感情的份上
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.05,0:18:00.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,破例不予以追究了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.20,0:18:01.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,母亲大人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.69,0:18:02.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秋穗小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.30,0:18:06.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了  姐姐  大哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.86,0:18:08.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恭喜了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.75,0:18:10.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能圆满收场  比什么都好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.30,0:18:15.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  又给裕人添麻烦了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.91,0:18:18.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真的是没用啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.38,0:18:21.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都说了  这话就不要说了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.52,0:18:23.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且  不是没用哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.35,0:18:28.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多亏了春香  我才能确定Cosplay咖啡店的服装
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.56,0:18:33.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才是不考虑你的安排  一味地依靠你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.36,0:18:34.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的很抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.77,0:18:35.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪有
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.45,0:18:39.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为这次的道歉  或者说道谢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.76,0:18:42.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次有什么我能帮的事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.29,0:18:45.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  那个…道谢的话
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.35,0:18:47.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都送了我这个八音盒
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.72,0:18:48.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和这个无关
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.04,0:18:51.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么都行哦  不用客气
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.56,0:18:52.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但  但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.37,0:18:57.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.84,0:19:01.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.51,0:19:03.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,土风舞
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.48,0:19:07.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白…白凤祭最后的土风舞
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.87,0:19:11.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果能和我一起跳的话我会很开心的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.55,0:19:16.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我  可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.29,0:19:18.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  我想和裕人一起跳
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.82,0:19:21.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或者说如果不是裕人的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.38,0:19:25.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不是裕人的话  我不要
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.34,0:19:29.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了  如果我可以的话
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.03,0:19:32.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真…真的吗  谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.38,0:19:36.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  哎呀  年轻真好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.21,0:19:40.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可不能错过啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.57,0:19:41.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,摄像准备
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.46,0:19:55.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害  有这么多资料的话  服装就没问题了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.45,0:19:57.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不愧是乃木坂同学
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.16,0:20:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关于时装也很在行呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.42,0:20:01.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.48,0:20:08.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的  这样无论如何也要让Cosplay咖啡店办成功
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.47,0:20:09.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噢噢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.73,0:20:20.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不愧是乃木坂同学  好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.60,0:20:21.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好疼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.67,0:21:10.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裕人  请加油
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.79,0:21:19.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.57,0:21:22.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.03,0:21:31.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呵呵～  给大哥哥的慰劳品吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.61,0:21:32.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.09,0:21:35.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天白凤祭就正式开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.48,0:21:38.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天会忙到比较晚的关系
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.89,0:21:40.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯～  原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.87,0:21:42.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亲手制作的饼干
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.69,0:21:49.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之  加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.83,0:21:50.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.63,0:22:04.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裕人  还在的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.28,0:22:06.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裕人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.72,0:22:08.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裕人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.65,0:22:34.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.84,0:22:36.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乃木坂同学
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.67,0:24:19.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「停滞」着的春香小姐  想要打开「永恒之门」
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.94,0:24:21.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行  姐姐不要去
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.85,0:24:23.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有欢乐和悲伤的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.93,0:24:24.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会让你去
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.02,0:24:27.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香小姐停止了时间
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.00,0:24:28.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.41,0:24:29.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下回
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.39,0:24:31.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「想要、在一起…」
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.46,0:24:33.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要记得看哦
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.22,0:24:34.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是最优先事项


